Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NAnother wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Falling like\Na star from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems that one\Nhad escaped my notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Even if I wanted to,\NI could never grant Ruko's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Releasing all of\Nthe LRIGs from their cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,simply isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And if I can't grant the wish,\Nthat means Tama couldn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But Ru still believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,She still persists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry we kind of\Njust let ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:00:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So, you're the one\Nwho wrote the novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NAs I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Fumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's crazy. I didn't\Nrealize you were so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're published?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, that's a\NFujikou High uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anybody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Cutting to the chase, which one\Nof you wants to battle first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you are one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A Selector!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:03:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I would be delighted to meet any\Nof you on the stage of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A high school author Selector,\Nrockin' a bad girl haircut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that is the most\Nawesome character ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm transforming into\NBurning Chorizo mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I think there's been a\Nmisunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here\Nto battle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for\Nbeing presumptuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,but what other reason could\NSelectors have to meet up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NJust because we're Selectors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean we have to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And now I'm beginning to\Nthink you're mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're saying none of you\Nhave a wish worth fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you win,\Nthey don't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Not how you'd think, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If you'll let us tell you\Nthe truth about this, Fumio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you might\Nchange your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Spreading the\Nnoble truth? I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an LRIG--Don't\Nact like you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am frightfully\Nwell-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm not\Nthe only one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me be frank:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,This "hidden truth"\Nbehind our wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And it still doesn't\Nchange my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I) "She is\Nthe ruler of White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,An almighty being\Nthat holds dominion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,over all WIXOSS Battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth lingers on\Nher lips, revealing the laws
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,of this twisted world".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,How much do you think\Nthis author really knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh. Aren't you just\Na barrel of laughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,No... that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN] Even if she knows\Nthe same facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean\Nshe has to come
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,to the same conclusion as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NYes, it's all quite cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,If a Selector loses three times,\Nher wish becomes tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But if she manages to\Nwin enough battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,it only serves to grant\Nfreedom to her LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Not truly free though,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,the LRIG must now grant\Nher former Selector's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That Selector, meanwhile,\Nbecomes imprisoned as an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If you know all that,\Nthen why keep battling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! No good can\Never come of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NInteresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You're among a chosen few,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,yet you deny your very\Nexistence as Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll admit, that's\Na new one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Plenty of Selectors have\Napproached me, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,All of 'em dying to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And after reading my novel,\Nhow could they resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhat do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because they\Nread your novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio, we don't want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But I do think you know\Nsomething about WIXOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,that we don't, and I'd\Nlike to hear what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NObtaining knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your wish then,\Nin a sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] You're a Selector,\Nso act like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle me for your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll tell you\Neverything you wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NI dunno, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing's ever free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,If it is worthwhile, there\Nis always struggle for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,However, I shall warn you\Nthat Fumio has never lost once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI haven't lost, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] Then unfortunately,\Nit'll lack the excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,of a higher-stakes battle,\Nbut on the upside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.36,Main,,0,0,0,,neither of us has much to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHey! Yoo-hoo, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,If Ruko wusses out, then\Nlet Chorizo give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,--[RUKO] Huh?\N--[YUZUKI] What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy... Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You realize you're out of the\Ngame after the next loss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NThat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not particular\Nabout my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NMe, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we have\Na battle on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Unless anyone objects, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--[CHIYORI] Woo-hoo!\N--[RUKO] No, let me fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE, CHIYORI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NRuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I kinda called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let Chiyori battle\Nsuch a strong player
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,when she's already\Nhad her second loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,She robbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NBe grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona. You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that your LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I, uh, nevermind, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO, RUKO]\NOpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN giggles]\NHow lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally time for a dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Damn it, we were\Njust supposed to talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I know Tama\Ntold me not to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's like I can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,The curtain rises,\Nnow let us enter the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon Code Maze\NTriumph and Clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Banish Triumphal Arch\Nwith Fallen Bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Your concern isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Just win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I use Slash Miracle\Nto Banish Puri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Then Puri's skill brings\NSurrelis to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Without Tama, she's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,She had better pull it\Ntogether and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NThat LRIG isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN] As usual,\Nyou're quick to catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't put my finger on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But somehow, she's\Ndifferent than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,--[FUMIO] Hmm...\N--[ANN] Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to get along\Nwith her Selector at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever power they\Npossess is wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] Then let's see if\Nwe can force it out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:41.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI'm-I'm gonna lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not just strong, she's\Nalways one step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\NI'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Well, for starters, why\Ndon't you stop cowering in fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] That's not\Nwhat I'm doing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Before, you had\Na hunger for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You had the conviction\Nto tear down any wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,to defy any limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna save your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now, you don't have\Nthe strength to save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NNot Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,and certainly not all the other\Ngirls transformed into LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI'll find a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No one should have to\Nsuffer like Hitoe did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Having such an innocent wish\Ntwisted into something so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Or Yuzuki, who fought and fought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.45,Main,,0,0,0,,only to have her whole\Nlife taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to end\Nthis game, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause you say it,\Ndoesn't make it true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It infuriates me that\NI lost to someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,who spews such\Nidealistic nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That I lost to an utter fool,\Nwho'd naïvely help others
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.22,Main,,0,0,0,,before herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That I lost to someone\Nso disgustingly pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYou have to find yourself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I became your LRIG\Nbecause I b elieved in you--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I knew you were strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So find that strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.77,Main,,0,0,0,,The strength you had\Nwhen you were with Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Or else, she'll be one more\Nfriend you fail to save!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NTama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a wish\Nworth fighting for,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and I don't care if\NI have to play this game
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll save my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] I know this sounds\Nironic coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,but this isn't a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because you have\Na character moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:42.43,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that you'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN]\NHaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't lose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIona, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--You're kidding.\N--[ANN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,She's at level four already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That's as high as it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What is she... doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NWhat the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything\Nlike this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NThis is it. Ruko's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what Tama felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What she believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN]\NThat's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you do that?!\NNobody can even do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! Yes! It's on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,A forbidden power that\Nawakens when the hero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,is backed into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Super exciting and super cliché!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Looks like Ruko's\Nfinally having fun again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NMm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though it took a Battle,\NI'm still happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhatever works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...I could ask...\Nto give me an encore...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, show's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANN whimpers]\NI gave it my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for what\Nyou said, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,And the whole transforming\Nthing was pretty awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did I tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I certainly\Nwasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Your LRIG's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,So, tell me, Iona, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear,\NI wasn't the one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,who told Fumio\Nabout Mayu, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She knew before we even met,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,about her and the room\Nand everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NBut how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't always Fumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Before this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...I was an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You... used to be an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NBut you became a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You won the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you wanna\Nbe a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something\Nwe don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It was for her, my Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NI did it to fulfill her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NAnd Fumio isn't my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But all of you know\Nhow that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Although we are apart now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,we are as bound by her\Nwish as the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NYou can... move around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG] You're watching me\Ndo it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,And you can talk, too--\Njust like a real girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG]\NKinda goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NHuh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG]\NActually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't seem too surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're more like "Oh, hey,\Nit's a talking card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,don't see that\Nevery day, huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)] Hmph.\NI read a lot of fantasy books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I've been conditioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I still need\Nto introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You can call me Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[LRIG]\NI can't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Call me whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Then from now on,\Nyour name's "Futase."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NWhoever I was before was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,For me, this was a new name\Nand a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE] You click and click and\Nclick on that thing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it really that much fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) sighs]\NNot really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Not right now at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The story isn't coming together,\Nso it's just frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NThen why don't you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) sighs] Because\Nit's really fun, sometimes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I love when I feel a real\Nsense of accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something that's\Nworth struggling for, Futase?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,If you mean like a wish,\Nor whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I try my best not to think\Nabout that kinda stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NSounds like something bad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.08,Main,,0,0,0,,happened to you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I won't\Npressure you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ever decide you\Nwanna talk, I'm here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ever look for\Nother Selectors to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] No matter how\Nmany times I asked her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I could never get her\Nto battle, even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR A]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What do mean you don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, but I\Nhave to achieve my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,with my own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR A] Hmph!\NWhatever, you little snob!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NOf course, she was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,If her wish was\Nsomething so simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,then an LRIG wouldn't\Nhave appeared before her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] And then,\Nthe guy lost his shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS B, C giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL D]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Like anyone's\Ngonna believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL F] It's true!\NI can show you the pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL D]\NWhoops! We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL E]\NDang it, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL F] Remind me to\Ntell you the rest after class!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL E] Go! Go! Go!\NI don't want detention!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL I]\NIs that a new card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL G]\NWell, this one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm about to\Nschool you with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL I]\NShow me what you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL H]\NI play winner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NYou bought a WIXOSS deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You could be playing\Nwith the other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You might have noticed that\NI'm not the best at socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NGoing to school day after day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and never talking\Nto anyone, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE] You can't\Nenjoy living like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, things are a lot\Nbetter lately, with you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Even you're smiling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE giggles]\NI guess it's contagious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NWhen I became an LRIG,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:35.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost everything, so it was\Neasy to become fixated on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,But as time passed,\Nthings changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NBefore I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I became as invested\Nin her wish as she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But then--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[door slams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:17:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO'S MOM]\NAnother overnighter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You think I don't know\Nwhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO'S DAD]\NWhat?! I was working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO'S MOM] You wanna stop\Nbeing an ass and settle this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO'S DAD]\NSure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon as you wanna\Ntalk about the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,you're screwing behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,--[glass shatters]\N--[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO'S MOM yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] Although she\Ntried to block it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,bit by bit, reality\Ngnawed away at her dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,and her one hope of escape
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,became yet another\Nsource of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR A]\NYou again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm here to win,\Nnot to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna battle\Nfor real, beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The situation has changed--I'm\Nready when you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NFumio...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR A] Oh yeah?\NYou shoulda said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You can still make your wish\Nhappen on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,if you keep fighting for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can and maybe I can't,\Nbut I'm fed up with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I could\Ndo things my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,but I'm just not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can't make\Nmy dream come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,there's no point\Nin living anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NI can't do this alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I need you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTASE]\NThen I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll fight and fight\Nfor your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.40,Main,,0,0,0,,with every ounce of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NThank you, Futase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:21.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm your LRIG, you know.\NThat's what I was born to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, let's start the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] Her initial reluctance\Nwas completely cast aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,She was an exceptional Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Always one step ahead\Nof her opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,unrelenting in the\Npursuit of her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL), FUTASE] I now\Naccept The Laws of the Selector
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,which state that with\Nthis sacred oath
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nwill now be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I did my best and now\Nmy wish comes true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll keep my promise,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL) gasps]\NFutase...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll fight for your wish with\Nevery ounce of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So please, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO (ORIGINAL)]\NNo. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] The girl who dreamed\Nof becoming a novelist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,was trapped inside\Na card instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NThe LRIG tasked with her wish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,was carried down\Nthe river of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,And soon, as those\Nwho came before her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,floated to the room where\Nthe girl of fate slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NDo you know the Girl of White?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So pure and innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,with a heart as warm\Nas the morning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But there is a\NGirl of Black as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Cruel and wicked, with a heart\Nas cold as the darkest night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She burns with jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Resenting every shining smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,that dances upon the cheeks\Nof the Girl of White.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...that bitter hatred turns\Nto thoughts of erasing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,her very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You think... all of that's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I sense something strange\Ncoming from your LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's unlike the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you the Girl of Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWha-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NDon't do it, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NYou're the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't dream of\Nbecoming the Girl of White.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,The light is not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It will stain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.24,Main,,0,0,0,,As gray as ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NThe Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:42.88,Main,,0,0,0,,The Girl of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"That Existence is Dark Black."
